31
00:01:30,380 --> 00:01:32,910
So what is stress?

32
00:01:32,910 --> 00:01:36,649
Essentially and really
simply, it's a recognition

33
00:01:36,650 --> 00:01:39,960
that we're unable to
cope with work demands.

34
00:01:39,960 --> 00:01:42,080
And it really can be
as simple as that.

35
00:01:42,080 --> 00:01:45,840
And there's a whole
variety of causes

36
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:47,231
that would make
us feel this way,

37
00:01:47,231 --> 00:01:48,729
and there's a whole
variety of signs

38
00:01:48,730 --> 00:01:53,040
that help us to see that we may
potentially be under stress.

39
00:01:53,040 --> 00:01:54,650
