44
00:02:08,449 --> 00:02:11,340
We've also got
long working hours.

45
00:02:11,340 --> 00:02:13,840
So look, we've all
done that at some point

46
00:02:13,840 --> 00:02:15,540
and worked those extra hours.

47
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:20,320
And in short periods of time
and for temporary projects

48
00:02:20,320 --> 00:02:21,970
or whatever, it's fine.

49
00:02:21,970 --> 00:02:23,859
But if that's a
long-term pattern,

50
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:26,340
that can really be an issue.

51
00:02:26,340 --> 00:02:29,840
We also have lack of support
from managers or coworkers.

52
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:32,840
No one really ever feels
like they're at work

53
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:35,150
